cdata.name: OctoCoin
cdata.desc: OCTO is a Counterparty asset with focus on decentralized website payments for Counterparty assets and Token Control Access Marketing. OCTO will create and fairly distribute a total of 88.8 million coinsto be used for early access and testing of the OCTO projects. Distributionincludes an alt coin burn, merged mining with FoldingCoin and a future crowd sale.
